OL,3,CCalls grow for Mandelson to return
OL,4,Cambassador severance pay
OL,6,FCalls are growing for Peter Mandelson
OL,7,Fto return the severance pay he
OL,8,Freceived after being sacked as
OL,9,FBritain's ambassador to the US over
OL,10,Fhis links to paedophile financier
OL,11,FJeffrey Epstein, as the prime minister
OL,12,Fadmitted "his mistake" over the
OL,13,Fappointment.
OL,15,FThe files, released on Thursday,
OL,16,Fshowed Mandelson was paid a package of
OL,17,Fnearly #75,000, made up of #40,330 as
OL,18,Fpay in lieu of notice, and a special
OL,19,Fseverance payment of #34,670 after he
OL,20,Fwas sacked.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
