OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773425166
OL,3,CCalls grow for Mandelson to return
OL,4,Cambassador severance pay
OL,6,FThe files also revealed Mandelson had
OL,7,Finitially asked to be paid out for the
OL,8,Fremainder of his four-year tenure as
OL,9,Fambassador, a sum which would have
OL,10,Ftotalled more than half a million
OL,11,Fpounds.
OL,13,FScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar
OL,14,FMandelson should "do the right thing"
OL,15,Fand return his severance payment as
OL,16,FTory leader Kemi Badenoch argued Lord
OL,17,FMandelson should not have received the
OL,18,F#75,000 payout.
OL,26,@vD@ROUvD@eO]
