OL,3,CCalls grow for Mandelson to return
OL,4,Cambassador severance pay
OL,6,FGovernment minister Darren Jones first
OL,7,Ftold MPs in parliament Mandelson
OL,8,Fshould donate the money to charity and
OL,9,Fon Thursday, his colleague in
OL,10,Fgovernment Nick Thomas-Symonds
OL,11,Fexpressed "moral outrage" over the
OL,12,Fpayment, seconding calls for the money
OL,13,Fto be donated to a victims' charity.
OL,15,FThe prime minister faced fresh
OL,16,Fquestions about his judgment in giving
OL,17,Fthe peer the ambassadorship despite
OL,18,Fbeing warned of a "general
OL,19,Freputational risk" because of his
OL,20,Frelationship with Epstein.
OL,26,@sD@KOUsD@YO]zD@SOU{D@RO]
