OL,3,CCalls grow for Mandelson to return
OL,4,Cambassador severance pay
OL,6,FOn Thursday, Starmer repeated his
OL,7,Fprevious apologies, taking
OL,8,Fresponsibility for his "mistake" in
OL,9,Fsending Lord Mandelson to Washington,
OL,10,Fas Downing Street denied there was a
OL,11,F"cover-up" in the release of files
OL,12,Frelated to the appointment.
OL,14,FSpeaking to reporters on Thursday from
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland, Starmer said: "It
OL,16,Fwas me that made the mistake... and
OL,17,Fit's me that makes the apology to the
OL,18,Fvictims of Epstein".
OL,26,@pD@XOUpD@`O]sD@AOUsD@JO]wD@aOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
