OL,3,CCalls grow for Mandelson to return
OL,4,Cambassador severance pay
OL,6,FIn his first public appearance since
OL,7,Fthe publication of the documents,
OL,8,FStarmer told reporters in Northern
OL,9,FIreland: "The release of the
OL,10,Finformation shows what was known.
OL,12,F"That led to further questions being
OL,13,Fasked.
OL,15,F"Unfortunately, because of the
OL,16,FMetropolitan Police investigation, we
OL,17,Fcan't release that information yet.
OL,26,@qD@JOUtD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
