OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773425166
OL,3,CCalls grow for Mandelson to return
OL,4,Cambassador severance pay
OL,6,F"But that doesn't take away from the
OL,7,Ffact that it was me that made a
OL,8,Fmistake, and it's me that makes the
OL,9,Fapology to the victims of Epstein, and
OL,10,FI do that."
OL,12,FQuestions have centred around what the
OL,13,Fprime minister knew, and when, after
OL,14,FStarmer's repeated assertion that
OL,15,FMandelson had lied to him during the
OL,16,Fappointment process.
OL,18,FBadenoch has called for Starmer to
OL,19,Fresign over his appointment of
OL,20,FMandelson.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]
