OL,3,CCalls grow for Mandelson to return
OL,4,Cambassador severance pay
OL,6,FSpeaking on Thursday, she said: "In
OL,7,Fany normal circumstances, the prime
OL,8,Fminister would be resigning.
OL,10,F"He's been shown to have lied to the
OL,11,FCommons. He told everyone that he did
OL,12,Fnot know the full extent of Peter
OL,13,FMandelson's relationship with the
OL,14,Fconvicted paedophile Jefrey Epstein,
OL,15,Fand now we can see from the release of
OL,16,Fthese files that that is not true.
OL,18,F"Labour MPs now need to consider their
OL,19,Fposition and ask themselves in good
OL,20,Fconscience, should this man be running
OL,21,Four country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
