OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773425166
OL,3,CCalls grow for Mandelson to return
OL,4,Cambassador severance pay
OL,6,F"He has shown a complete lack of
OL,7,Fjudgment, catastrophic error after
OL,8,Fcatastrophic error."
OL,10,FIn February, Starmer said he regretted
OL,11,Fappointing Mandelson, saying: "If I
OL,12,Fknew then what I know now, he would
OL,13,Fnever have been anywhere near
OL,14,Fgovernment."
OL,16,F"In any normal circumstances, the
OL,17,Fprime minister would be resigning,"
OL,18,Fsaid Badenoch as she accused the PM of
OL,19,Flying to MPs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
