OL,3,CCalls grow for Mandelson to return
OL,4,Cambassador severance pay
OL,6,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said:
OL,7,F"There will be people looking at the
OL,8,Fsum of money he was paid, saying he
OL,9,Fshouldn't have got it."
OL,11,F"We would prefer, as the government,
OL,12,Fthat he either paid it back or, better
OL,13,Fstill, donated it to a charity that
OL,14,Fsupports victims of violence against
OL,15,Fwomen and girls," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
