OL,3,CCalls grow for Mandelson to return
OL,4,Cambassador severance pay
OL,6,F"What I can tell you is that the
OL,7,Freason that money was paid out at all
OL,8,Fwas because the alternative was a
OL,9,Fpotentially costly legal battle that
OL,10,Fwould have cost the taxpayer even more
OL,11,Fthan that sum of money.
OL,13,FHe added: "I hope Peter Mandelson will
OL,14,Fdo the right thing and either return
OL,15,Fit or, better still, donate it to
OL,16,Fcharity."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
