OL,4,Cambassador severance pay
OL,6,FSpeaking to Good Morning Britain,
OL,7,FWomen's MinisterJess Phillips, backed
OL,8,Fthe PM's apology, saying Starmer had
OL,9,Fmade it "incredibly clear, that it was
OL,10,Fa terrible mistake".
OL,12,F"There is nobody, no prime minister
OL,13,Fcertainly that I've ever worked under,
OL,14,Feither on the frontline or now, who I
OL,15,Fhave ever found as much of an ally on
OL,16,Fviolence against women and girls," she
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
