OL,6,FThe Minister for Violence Against
OL,7,FWomen and Girls, Jess Phillips, backed
OL,8,Fthe prime minister's record when asked
OL,9,Fabout his judgment in appointing Peter
OL,10,FMandelson.
OL,12,FThomas-Symonds did admit the due
OL,13,Fdiligence report detailing Mandelson's
OL,14,Fconnections to Epstein raised "serious
OL,15,Fquestions".
OL,17,F"The prime minister then did put those
OL,18,Fquestions to Lord Mandelson. The prime
OL,19,Fminister has said he was misled. He
OL,20,Fdeeply regrets believing the
OL,21,Freassurances he was given.
