OL,6,F"He has apologised for believing what
OL,7,Fwas said to him by Peter Mandelson."
OL,9,FThe documents and messages showing
OL,10,Fboth the follow-up questions the prime
OL,11,Fminister asked and Mandelson's
OL,12,Fresponse were not included in the
OL,13,Fbatch of documents released on
OL,14,FThursday, as the police had advised
OL,15,Fthey could prejudice their ongoing
OL,16,Finvestigation into the former
OL,17,Fambassador.
