OL,6,FThe Prime Minister did not write any
OL,7,Fnotes on the document, therefore
OL,8,Fnothing was redacted, ITV News
OL,9,Funderstands.
OL,11,FThe PM's official spokesman told
OL,12,Freporters: "I refute the suggestion of
OL,13,Fa cover-up. The government has
OL,14,Fcomplied fully. I just don't accept
OL,15,Fthat it's the case at all.
OL,17,F"There are a range of different ways
OL,18,Fin which the prime minister's senior
OL,19,Fteam responds to advice.
OL,26,@tD@LOUyD@AOU
