OL,6,FDowning Street said: "The prime
OL,7,Fminister did read the advice, but
OL,8,Fclearly there are lessons to be
OL,9,Flearned on the wider appointment
OL,10,Fprocesses, and the processes that led
OL,11,Fup to them."
OL,13,FSpeaking on Thursday, Badenoch
OL,14,Frepeated similar comments she had made
OL,15,Fon Wednesday.
OL,17,F"The comments which Keir Starmer would
OL,18,Fhave put on the box notes ` those are
OL,19,Fthe cover notes where you explain what
OL,20,Fyou want to happen ` are missing.
